28,"created":"09:43:48","title":"作为程序员，留在美国还是回国？","author":"MID","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/MID","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/20af/c7ff/523581_mini.png?m=1639076854"},{"id":846046,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1647188067","description":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/846046","replies":87,"created_ts":1649564038,"created":"12:13:58","title":"大家觉得是居家办公工作效率更高，还是去公司更高呢？","author":"KURANADO","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/KURANADO","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b8ce/c158/282351_mini.png?m=1517992357"},{"id":846115,"node":"硬件","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/hardware","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9a11/5815/52_mini.png?m=1630576655","description":"接上帖 <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"/t/845887\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">/t/845887</a><br /><br />在研究快充协议的时候，无意间发现无论是充电头自带的数据线还是购物网站上常见的快充线，其数据传输速率基本是最高 480 Mbps ，都在宣传“大电流”，对传输速率却一笔带过，甚至还有宣传 480 Mbps 快的……<br /><br />本来还想吐槽大部分数码产品的商品详情页没用的信息过多，而我关注具体的具体参数都在最后甚至是没有，直到我看到了这个评论，才发现不能把自己知道的事情当常识……<br /><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"/i/2m75CUtP.jpeg\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"在新窗口打开图片 2m75CUtP.jpeg\"><img src=\"//i.v2ex.co/2m75CUtP.jpeg\" class=\"embedded_image\"></a>","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/846115","replies":86,"created_ts":1649591567,"created":"19:52:47","title":"为什么现在标榜“快充”的数据线其数据传输速率跌回了 USB 2.0 时代的 480 Mbps？","author":"Jat001","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Jat001","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9457/afe7/29991_mini.png?m=1648043417"},{"id":846136,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1649311216","description":"<ul>\n<li>我是一名大二的学生，对这个计算机软考中级的考试也不是特别的了解，想请教一下大佬们。</li>\n<li>对于这个软考，我不考研，这个对找工作有帮助吗，或者他以后有其他的用处吗？</li>\n<li>请求大佬解答，感谢！！！</li>\n</ul>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/846136","replies":74,"created_ts":1649598074,"created":"21:41:14","title":"计算机的软考","author":"ha2ha","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/ha2ha","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ea73/8b59/561979_mini.png?m=1640073432"},{"id":846040,"node":"上海","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/shanghai","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6f49/22f4/18_mini.png?m=1648461116","description":"7*24 小时维护库存。货品一直更新补充<br /><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://u.jd.com/WdlYGfm\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://u.jd.com/WdlYGfm</a><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://u.jd.com/WwlYK96\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://u.jd.com/WwlYK96</a><br /><br />其它地方看到的，有 aff","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/846040","replies":65,"created_ts":1649562076,"created":"11:41:16","title":"京东上海保供专场","author":"o0","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/o0","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1fa3fcc2628f8deaa00743ae8ccf600e?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":846137,"node":"职场话题","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/career","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1649600540","description":"<p>几年前入学（伦敦大学金史密斯学院）的时候托福我考了 97 ，这几年来也是在努力的学英语，无论是日常生活还是读写文档、文章都没有问题。但是我还没上过班，希望 v2ers 能看看我的简历在中国能找到什么样的工作 /实习。</p>\n<p>简历 URL: <a href=\"https://0x0.st/obdH.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://0x0.st/obdH.pdf</a></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/846137","replies":62,"created_ts":1649598412,"created":"21:46:52","title":"大家看看我这样的简历能在中国找到什么样的工作？","author":"aleisterw","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/aleisterw","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/2905/7c51/540885_mini.png?m=1649597614"},{"id":846088,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1647188067","description":"<p>打搅各位，几年前把一部字典移植到了 macOS 内置 Dictionary.app ，一直放在 onedrive ，陆陆续续总有人发信问：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>链接又失效了</li>\n<li>下载很慢很慢</li>\n<li>有没有百度盘链接</li>\n<li>你能不能发给我</li>\n</ol>\n<p>这很尴尬，请教大家，未知 2022 年的当下，国内哪家云盘对用户友好，又不需要我自己操心，还免费（抱歉，没有预算放这上面）。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/846088","replies":41,"created_ts":1649578577,"created":"16:16:17","title":"询问：国内简洁好用无需客户端的云盘","author":"placeless","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/placeless","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/02bc/ce14/19199_mini.png?m=1473161850"},{"id":845991,"node":"Jekyll","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/jekyll","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1068/c6e4/410_mini.png?m=1633248911","description":"理由：<br /><br />1 写 hexo 步骤太繁琐了 每次都要写好 md  然后复制到家里的电脑，开着代理，git push ，步骤太多已经让人懒得提交到博客了  甚至有时候写完就放本地了<br /><br />2 hexo 的环境难跨设备，这次重装系统，老的环境没了，虽然文章内容 md 还在，但是已经没法提交新文章了（工程环境没了，要从头搭建）<br /><br />3 据说 Jekyll 能达到和 hexo 一样的效果，但是绝对的优势是可以只提交 md ，剩下的事在线生成。也就是说我可以直接在 github 网页端提交 md 文件就能实现文章的更新。我第一次部署好之后，甚至工程环境就可以放心大胆的丢掉了，毕竟平时不需要修改什么，以后只改 md 文件<br /><br />4 主题也不少看了几个挺满意的<br /><br />5 还有什么坑是我没考虑到的吗?","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/845991","replies":39,"created_ts":1649531370,"created":"03:09:30","title":"想把博客从 hexo 迁移到 Jekyll 了","author":"wasd6267016","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/wasd6267016","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ba2d/959a/200647_mini.png?m=1649606470"},{"id":846023,"node":"Linux","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/linux","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_mini.png?m=1635654665","description":"<p>昨天收到 <a href=\"https://github.com/tuna/issues/issues/1466#event-6401872903\" rel=\"nofollow\">Github 镜像请求通过</a> 的好消息，\n现在 Arch Linux 已被国内镜像站检索、可<a href=\"https://mirrorz.org/os/ArchLinuxGUI\" rel=\"nofollow\">极速下载</a></p>\n<p>特别感谢 ZenithalHourlyRate 的帮助！</p>\n<p><img alt=\"截图\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/arch-linux-gui/web@master/img/Ss/installer.png\"/></p>\n<p>Arch Linux GUI 旨在提供含有多种可选桌面环境的原版 Arch 系统，\n采用了开源的、图形化的 Calamares Linux 安装器 ( 也被如 Manjaro  等发行版采用了 ) </p>\n<p>几乎只需要地区语言、分区、用户信息三步设置即可安装！\n甚至可以根据 <a href=\"https://github.com/calamares/calamares/wiki/Deploy-Configuration\" rel=\"nofollow\">Wiki</a> 实现高级自动化、定制化部署</p>\n<p>🙏 愿世上再也没有难以安装的 Arch Linux~</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/846023","replies":36,"created_ts":1649558052,"created":"10:34:12","title":"Arch Linux 图形化简易安装器已被镜像站收录","author":"LittleboyHarry","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/LittleboyHarry","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3a40/b9bd/434693_mini.png?m=1649557887"},{"id":846106,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","description":"<p>为了 64g 内存上的 m1 max ，如果不跑图形相关的东西，这两个核心对我来说是不是都没啥区别。<br/>\n另外 apple care 有必要么？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/846106","replies":32,"created_ts":1649585070,"created":"18:04:30","title":"写代码选 m1 max 24 核还是 32 核？","author":"agdhole","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/agdhole","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e32578262dfb4ca9a14999f8ed61a4e5?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":846056,"node":"深圳","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/shenzhen","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3c59/dc04/21_mini.png?m=1648461133","description":"<p>希望通勤 30min 以内的，目前看了感觉南头那边好一点，或者西丽那边，不知道有没有可以推荐的地方呀？提前谢谢大家</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/846056","replies":29,"created_ts":1649567660,"created":"13:14:20","title":"到深圳实习，在科苑那边上班，大佬们推荐下租房地点呀","author":"fs11zhuangb","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/fs11zhuangb","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e78a/22a6/280624_mini.png?m=1517908611"},{"id":846043,"node":"MacBook Pro","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/mbp","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d3d9/4468/10_mini.png?m=1630643933","description":"<p>本人使用的是 2021 款 14.2 寸 MacBookpro ，看文字时间久了容易眼睛不聚焦，文字有点虚，想问问各位，你们使用久了会不会有这种情况，最早使用 Windows 笔记本不存在这种情况，自从 2019 年用 16 寸的时候会有这种感觉，后来就卖了，去年新款出来以后看到是 mingled 屏幕，想着应该会改善，没想到用久了还是会有点模糊眼花，不知道是眼睛的问题还是屏幕的问题，想问问大家的看法。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/846043","replies":29,"created_ts":1649562674,"created":"11:51:14","title":"Mac book pro 视网膜屏幕看久了眼花","author":"zyy109","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/zyy109","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/97ff1366aa69bdd5